        Add explicit post-composition slots: located_in, laterality,          
  therapeutic_agent                                                           
                                                                              
        Schema changes:                                                       
        - Add LateralityEnum (LEFT, RIGHT, BILATERAL)                         
        - Add located_in slot for anatomical location qualifiers              
        - Add laterality slot for laterality qualifiers                       
        - Add therapeutic_agent slot for specifying drugs in treatments       
